{
  "text": "Having confirmed the spectroscopic similarities between the addition of TfOH and Sc(OTf) 3 to 1, the Brønsted acid assisted oxidation [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] of styrene was examined. Essentially identical catalytic behavior was observed when using TfOH or Sc(OTf) [CITATION_4] , including a lag period followed by rapid onset of H 2 O 2 decomposition and oxidation of styrene ( Figure 3) .",
